{
  "message": "test(fuzz): extend column_arith corpus with 6 IEEE-754 edge-case seeds\n\nAppend 6 column_arith fuzz seeds covering arithmetic edge cases that\nshould produce well-defined IEEE-754 results:\n\n- mul_inf_zero: INF * 0.0 -> NaN\n- pow_neg_zero_zero: (-0.0)**0.0 -> 1.0 (IEEE convention)\n- mod_negative_negative: -2 % -1 (Rust + pandas modulo on negatives)\n- sub_nan_int: NaN - int -> NaN (NaN propagation)\n- floordiv_neg_inf_pos_inf: -INF // INF -> NaN\n- add_null_finite: Null + scalar -> Null (missing propagation)\n\nEach seed exercises fuzz_column_arith_bytes which verifies oracle\nparity against the in-Rust scalar arithmetic kernel for the chosen op.\n\n[bd-frankenpandas-hkj82]\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>",
